{"id": 61212, "date": "2025-10-24T04:00:40", "date_gmt": "2025-10-24T11:00:40", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61212"}, "modified": "2026-06-13T14:47:18", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-13T21:47:18", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-october-24-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/24/kingdom-of-days-october-24-2/", "title": {"rendered": "October 24"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1970:\u00a0</strong>Steel Mill is among the three top bands from a summer festival invited back to perform at the Municipal Auditorium in Nashville.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54789\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/the_tennessean_1970_10_18_page_162/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162.jpg?fit=1397%2C1209&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1397,1209\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162.jpg?fit=758%2C656&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-54789 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162.jpg?resize=758%2C656&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"656\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162.jpg?w=1397&amp;ssl=1 1397w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162.jpg?resize=300%2C260&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162.jpg?resize=1024%2C886&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/The_Tennessean_1970_10_18_Page_162.jpg?resize=768%2C665&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play a River Tour show at the Seattle Center Coliseum. Distributed at the show: the first issue of\u00a0<em>Backstreets,\u00a0</em>a four-page fanzine published by local fan Charles R. Cross. Over the four decades that follow,\u00a0<em>Backstreets </em>will evolve and thrive as a magazine, web site, and online community dedicated to bringing together Springsteen fans from around the world.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pRVAyY8cQqM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22434\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/backstreets/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/backstreets.jpg?fit=1600%2C1600&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1600,1600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_time